Enum Class ProductDataFieldDefinition

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ProductDataFieldDefinition>

Serializable, Comparable<ProductDataFieldDefinition>, Constable
public enum ProductDataFieldDefinition extends Enum<ProductDataFieldDefinition>
The ProductDataFieldDefinition contains the data fields used to populate the open metadata digital product data dictionary and data specs.
